````` ::: ::: ## Part 2 ### Bike Family ::: {.cell hash='02_data_acquisition_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-4_7573038b4980c78be08dac7f13aad66f'} ```{.r .cell-code} #3.2 url_home <- "https://www.rosebikes.com/bikes" bikes_home <- url_home %>% read_html() bike_family_tbl <- bikes_home %>% html_nodes(css = ".catalog-navigation__link")%>% html_attr('title') %>% discard(.p = ~stringr::str_detect(.x, "Bikes with short delivery times"))%>% enframe(name = "position", value = "family_class") %>% mutate(family_id = str_glue("#{family_class}"))%>% mutate(url = glue("https://www.rosebikes.com/bikes/{family_class}")) bike_family_tbl ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} `````{=html}
````` ::: ::: ### Get Data ::: {.cell hash='02_data_acquisition_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-5_a96bc74a86eae271bc5310d6be88786b'} ```{.r .cell-code} bike_category_url <- bike_family_tbl$url[1] html_bike_category <- read_html(bike_category_url) get_bike_data <- function(url){ html_bike_category <- read_html(url) bike_category_url <- bike_family_tbl$url[1] html_bike_category <- read_html(bike_category_url) #urls bike_url_tbl <- html_bike_category %>% html_nodes(css =".catalog-category-bikes__button") %>% html_attr("href") %>% str_remove(pattern = "\\?.*") %>% enframe(name = "position",value = "part_url") %>% mutate(url = glue("https://www.rosebikes.com{part_url}")) bike_url_tbl #Bike Names bike_name_tbl <- html_bike_category %>% html_nodes(".basic-headline__title") %>% html_text() %>% str_remove(pattern = "\\n") %>% str_remove(pattern = "\"") %>% enframe(name = "position", value = "Name") bike_name_tbl #descriptions bike_desc_tbl <- html_bike_category %>% html_nodes(".catalog-category-bikes__content-subtitle") %>% html_text() %>% str_remove(pattern = "\\n") %>% str_remove(pattern = "\"") %>% enframe(name = "position", value = "Description") #prices bike_price_tbl <- html_bike_category %>% html_nodes(".catalog-category-bikes__price-title") %>% html_text() %>% str_remove(pattern = "\\n") %>% str_remove(pattern = "\"") %>% enframe(name = "position", value = "Price") %>% left_join(bike_desc_tbl, by = character()) %>% left_join(bike_name_tbl, by = character()) %>% left_join(bike_url_tbl, by = character()) %>% select(Name, url, Description, Price) %>% as_tibble() bike_price_tbl } ``` ::: ### Loop ::: {.cell hash='02_data_acquisition_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-6_35ccb7d661c5ac1234d3fde042b26575'} ```{.r .cell-code} rose_bike_data_tbl <- tibble() for(i in seq_along(bike_family_tbl$url)){ bike_category_url <- bike_family_tbl$url[i] rose_bike_data_tbl <- bind_rows(rose_bike_data_tbl, get_bike_data(bike_category_url)) Sys.sleep(5) print(i) } ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr} ``` #> Warning: Using `by = character()` to perform a cross join was deprecated in dplyr 1.1.0. #>
